                                  BUSINESS
                       'HARTFORD AMONG TOP NET CITIES'
               --Hartford Business Journal, November 20, 2000

                        Picture of Downtown Hartford
                   State House Square - Downtown Hartford

   "For the second consecutive year Hartford is the only city in the
   Northeast ranking in the first 30 of the top 40 real estate markets for
   business attraction, snagging 17th place in the August issue of
   Expansion Magazine."  --Hartford Business Journal, August 21, 2000

   The newly established Hartford Economic Development Commission is the
   City's "business arm."  The following organizations and web sites are
   also excellent resources for business and economic development:

